name: Get in faster than me 48,18867 sec
name_original: Get in faster than me 48,18867 sec
description:
Hello everyone. Thank you for wasting your time on me. I will answer a popular question of my friends: "Why did I take so long to complete this game?" BECAUSE I WASN'T IN A HURRY. My best record is 14,504, but my friend's best record is 8.743232.

This project was created within the framework of "Mini Jam 123: Web".
And it's also my first game that I've released. I hope you enjoy my project and you will spend your precious time on it :3
